  m_Name: D4E8 Dialogue
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  dialogueHidesSubmit: 0
  lines:
  - H-hi mister!..... I think this should be everything you uh, need!
  - 'You: You ok? You seem, stressed.'
  - "Oh I\u2019m just\u2026 a bit scared, ever since my mum went through a few days
    ago, I haven\u2019t even been able to contact her."
  - "I really hope she\u2019s ok, shouldn\u2019t they have computers, or something
    over there? Can\u2019t she just send me one message?"
  - "I miss her\u2026.. I just, want to be with her again."
  - "You: Once you pass through, I\u2019m sure she\u2019ll be waiting for you right
    at the gates. Don\u2019t worry, you\u2019ll be ok."
  - "T-thank you mister, you\u2019re very kind"
